<section id="JCR.TransactionManagerLookup">
  <title>TransactionManagerLookup</title>

  <para>The TransactionManagerLookup of Infinispan can be registered as an eXo
  container component in the <emphasis>configuration.xml</emphasis> file as
  next:</para>

  <programlisting language="xml">&lt;component&gt;
   &lt;key&gt;org.infinispan.transaction.lookup.TransactionManagerLookup&lt;/key&gt;
   &lt;type&gt;org.exoplatform.services.transaction.infinispan.JBossStandaloneJTAManagerLookup&lt;/type&gt;
&lt;/component&gt;</programlisting>
</section>
